        ===========
        This project use `sykel` for release handling etc: https://pypi.org/project/sykel/
        
        Resources
        =========
        
        REST interface
        --------------
        Check the routes file in the git-annex repo (under assistant/webapp) to get an
        understanding about the REST interface.
        
        Misc
